        <p><strong>Lines:</strong> 3 – 14</p>
        <p><strong>Impact:</strong> Hard to maintain & debug</p>
      </div>

      <div class="suggestion">
        <h2>Refactoring Suggestion</h2>
        <p><strong>Suggestion:</strong> Extract Method</p>
        <p><strong>Why this helps:</strong><br>
          Improves readability, reuse, and testability without changing logic.
        </p>

        <button class="apply">Apply Refactor</button>
        <button class="ignore">Ignore</button>
      </div>

